transcription: Apparently the Turks are the horniest and naughtiest of all of us, which has kind of surprised me. And then second in place, who would have guessed, good old fucking Australia. 13.3 chicks, that's what apparently we get. And when you look at that, you'd be like, okay, dozen or so partners, and maybe a few of those would be long-term partners, and one of them maybe would be the long, long-term partner. And a few flings and a couple of one-night stands, and okay, that seems kind of reasonable for an average person. But it's an average. What that means, I would say, now don't quote me on the stats here, but there's going to be some people who hoard the sex, me and a number of men that I've met throughout my career. And so that stands to reason, if there's one guy who's having sex with 100 different girls, but then that's taking away all of his sex from lots of other guys. So on the other outlier end, there must be lots of guys who have no sex or once or very, very little sex. There is a problem with that idea too, which is that sex is not a finite resource.
